OL,3,CThree dead puppies found dumped in
OL,4,Cbags on roadside
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,7,Fafter three dead puppies were dumped
OL,8,Fin carrier bags next to a road in
OL,9,FSouth Yorkshire.
OL,11,FThe French bulldogs were found on an
OL,12,Fembankment in a layby on the A616 in
OL,13,FWortley, Barnsley.
OL,15,FSouth Yorkshire Police said the
OL,16,Fanimals, which were blond in colour,
OL,17,Fare believed to have been left there
OL,18,Fovernight.
