OL,3,CThree dead puppies found dumped in
OL,4,Cbags on roadside
OL,6,FForensic tests are being carried out
OL,7,Fto try to determine where they came
OL,8,Ffrom.
OL,10,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,11,Fcall police on 101.
